{
  "stem": "16790.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was tremendous-- and they-- I remember the meetings that they would hold to discuss these things, to talk about what-- what were the possible causes of action.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The passengers, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they held meetings sometimes twice a day to-- to find out what-- what's going on.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they would disseminate the news and-- and talk about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my mother, you know, she was so sick she-- [SIGHS] there was nothing-- she was more concerned about her sickness, her seasickness than anything else.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she felt everything was gonna be OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But somehow, she got-- pulled herself together and got to the purser.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And from-- from what I understand, she talked to the purser into getting us to go to England.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I honestly don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She-- she claimed that-- that she talked to the purser and-- and convinced him that because that she had just her mother and two-- two-- two small children that she should be able to go to-- to England.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did give us onto the thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whether she bribed him, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know where she would get something to bribe him with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But she-- she did manage to get us to go to England.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she felt that the only safe place for us would be on the-- off the continent and-- and onto England itself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm assuming because we got called in December of '39 that we were high on the list.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we left in May of '39 and we were-- in June of '39 we were in Havana and six months later, our number came up.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I'm assuming from that information that we were high on the list.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's interesting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
